 to help the Sathirian army.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5196,'Firemyst Supply Stocking','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I have offered to assist the supply sergeant with his supply shortage.',0,'I completed the supplies the supply sergeant required. <br>','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5197,'Promises Kept','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I started my investigation on the traditional crafts of Rivervale because of the sarnak Danelak\'s curiosity about the old region. It would behoove me to remember my promises and return to tell him what I learned.',0,'I remembered my promise to bring news of Rivervale to Danelak. He was very happy to hear my tale, and rewarded me with a fine cloak.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5198,'Shipyard Building Work','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I have offered to assist the Far Seas Trading Company in building their new ship.',0,'I provided some of the components required to build the new ship. <br>','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5199,'Crafting Apprentice','Tradeskill','Unknown',30,30,'The crafting guild has requested that I take on an apprentice to instruct.',0,'I met with my crafting guild about taking on an apprentice.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5200,'In A Bind','Tradeskill','Unknown',50,50,'Meledi Augren wants to become a writer, and she\'s asked me to make her a notebook to write in.',0,'I discovered how to make notebooks that can be written in.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5201,'[NO NAME]','Tradeskill','Unknown',90,90,'[NO BASE TEXT]',0,'[NO COMPLETED TEXT]','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5202,'[NO NAME]','Tradeskill','Unknown',90,90,'[NO BASE TEXT]',0,'[NO COMPLETED TEXT]','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5203,'[NO NAME]','Tradeskill','Unknown',90,90,'[NO BASE TEXT]',0,'[NO COMPLETED TEXT]','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5204,'[NO NAME]','Tradeskill','Unknown',90,90,'[NO BASE TEXT]',0,'[NO COMPLETED TEXT]','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua'),(5205,'[NO NAME]','Tradeskill','Unknown',90,90,'[N