e been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Commonlands/FarSeasRequisitionWC077.lua'),(5216,'Far Seas Requisition - WC 045','The Commonlands','The Commonlands',20,1,'I have discovered a Far Seas Requisition slip. The hunter charged with filling the order must have been slain. It looks like this order was placed by Taskmaster Kozma in The Commonlands. If I hunt down the creatures and fill the order I can deliver the order to the Taskmaster for a reward.',330260,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster at the crossroads in the Commonlands. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Commonlands/FarSeasRequisitionWC045.lua'),(5217,'A Strange Stone Wedge','The Commonlands','The Commonlands',18,1,'I\'ve found a dull chipped hatchet head and while normally such things would be thrown away quickly this may prove to be useful once remade.',0,'I finished remaking Chickenbane.','Quests/Commonlands/AStrangeStoneWedge.lua'),(5218,'Bloodskull Orc Bounty   ','The Commonlands','The Commonlands',14,1,'I found a bounty issued by the Freeport Militia calling for able citizens to aid in the resistance against the Bloodskull threat. The bounty promises a generous reward to those who give a lot of twenty Bloodskull earrings to Captain Vrondell as proof of their contribution.',5590132,'I found a bounty issued by the Freeport Militia calling for able citizens to aid in the resistance against the orcish threat. I acquired ten Bloodskull earrings, quite blood stained, and brought them to Captain Vrondell. I was awarded for my contribution to the cause.','Quests/Commonlands/BloodskullOrcBounty.lua');
